Um6ss99Kv0T_QuC8KLF], and while it=E2=80=99s hard to know exactly how many =
people use Excel regularly, estimates put it at 750 million users [https://=
email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUcuO5CAM_JpwI-KZkEMOq93Z23xDxMPdQUMgAjI9-fsl6c=
