t%20important%20consumer%20product%20.]. By comparison, as of 2018, there w=
ere only 10.7 million Javascript developers and 7 million Python developers=
 [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxlUsuO3CAQ_BpzG4uHsfGBQ5LdHHLNB1gYembQ=
