 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">But the enduring, passionate =
user fervor for the product isn&#8217;t even its most unique attribute. Exc=
el&#8217;s most lasting impact extends beyond the spreadsheet itself.</p><p=
 style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1=
em 0;"><strong>Excel may be the most influential software ever built.</stro=
ng> It is a canonical example of <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/=
c/eJxFkM1uhDAMhJ-GHFH-CYccWlV7as89opAYNlpIUEgW8fbNLodKli15ZI_msybDHNOpt7hn9=
