ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">In 1982, Kapor left to bu=
ild a yet-to-be-named product that combined the spreadsheet with graphing, =
and somehow convinced Personal Software to carve the product out of his non=
-compete. &#8220;I am not sure why they agreed to this,&#8221; he <a href=
=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMuOhSAMhp_msDTchQWL2cxrGC5VyVEwgG=
N8-2GOi0matmnT_vk_bxssudzmyLWhvzS1-wCT4KobtAYFnRXKFIMhkiomuEbB8ECUUCjWaS4Au=
42baeUEdJxui962mNPnAmMq0GosCBucmAl2ngfuiSByppYSpzHMZHx07RkiJA8GfqDcOQHazNra=
